statements: SELECT * FROM telepsychiatry_sessions;
SELECT session_id, session_date, session_duration FROM telepsychiatry_sessions;
SELECT * FROM telepsychiatry_sessions WHERE session_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT session_id, session_duration FROM telepsychiatry_sessions WHERE psychiatrist_id = 123;
SELECT session_id, patient_id, session_date, session_notes FROM telepsychiatry_sessions WHERE session_duration > 30;
SELECT * FROM telepsychiatry_sessions WHERE patient_id = 1;
SELECT session_id, session_date, session_duration FROM telepsychiatry_sessions WHERE psychiatrist_id = 3 ORDER BY session_date DESC;
SELECT session_id, session_date, session_notes FROM telepsychiatry_sessions WHERE session_duration > 30 AND session_notes LIKE '%progress%' ORDER BY session_date ASC;
SELECT patient_id, psychiatrist_id, COUNT(session_id) AS num_sessions FROM telepsychiatry_sessions GROUP BY patient_id, psychiatrist_id HAVING num_sessions >= 5;
SELECT DISTINCT patient_id FROM telepsychiatry_sessions WHERE session_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-04-30';
SELECT session_id, patient_id, therapist_id, session_date, duration_minutes FROM telepsychiatry_sessions;
SELECT therapist_id, patient_id, session_date, session_id, duration_minutes FROM telepsychiatry_sessions;
SELECT * FROM telepsychiatry_sessions WHERE therapist_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001';
SELECT session_id, recording_url, recording_duration_minutes FROM session_recordings;
SELECT session_id, recording_url, recording_duration_minutes, recording_date FROM session_recordings WHERE recording_duration_minutes > 30;
SELECT * FROM telepsychiatry_sessions ORDER BY session_date DESC;
SELECT therapist_id, COUNT(session_id) FROM telepsychiatry_sessions GROUP BY therapist_id;
SELECT * FROM telepsychiatry_sessions WHERE duration_minutes > 30 AND session_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT therapist_id, AVG(duration_minutes) FROM telepsychiatry_sessions GROUP BY therapist_id HAVING AVG(duration_minutes) > 45;
SELECT patient_id, therapist_id, session_date FROM telepsychiatry_sessions WHERE session_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30';
SELECT * FROM telepsychiatry_sessions;
SELECT session_id, therapist_id, start_time, end_time FROM telepsychiatry_sessions WHERE duration_minutes > 30;
SELECT session_id, patient_id, start_time, end_time, duration_minutes FROM telepsychiatry_sessions ORDER BY start_time DESC;
SELECT session_id, therapist_id, start_time, end_time FROM telepsychiatry_sessions WHERE therapist_id = 5;
SELECT session_id, therapist_id, start_time, end_time FROM telepsychiatry_sessions WHERE therapist_id = 3 OR therapist_id = 4;
SELECT * FROM telepsychiatry_sessions;
SELECT session_id, therapist_id, start_time FROM telepsychiatry_sessions WHERE therapist_id = 12 ORDER BY start_time DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT session_id, rating FROM session_feedback WHERE rating > 3 ORDER BY rating ASC, session_id DESC;
SELECT session_id, recording_url FROM session_recordings WHERE recording_duration_minutes > 30 ORDER BY recording_duration_minutes DESC, session_id ASC;
SELECT therapist_id, COUNT(session_id) AS session_count FROM telepsychiatry_sessions GROUP BY therapist_id ORDER BY session_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM session_records;
SELECT session_id, therapist_id, patient_id FROM session_records WHERE session_date = '2022-01-01';
SELECT therapist_name FROM therapist_records WHERE therapist_license_number = '123456';
SELECT patient_name, patient_gender FROM patient_records ORDER BY patient_date_of_birth DESC;
SELECT session_id, therapist_id, note FROM session_notes WHERE note_date >= '2022-01-01 00:00:00';
SELECT * FROM session_records;
SELECT session_id, session_date, session_duration FROM session_records ORDER BY session_date DESC;
SELECT t.therapist_name, p.patient_name, s.session_date FROM therapist_records t JOIN session_records s ON t.therapist_id = s.therapist_id JOIN patient_records p ON p.patient_id = s.patient_id;
SELECT * FROM therapist_records WHERE therapist_license_number LIKE 'ABC%';
SELECT s.session_id, s.session_date, n.note FROM session_records s LEFT JOIN session_notes n ON s.session_id = n.session_id;
SELECT * FROM telepsychiatry_sessions;
SELECT session_id, session_date, therapist_id FROM telepsychiatry_sessions WHERE patient_id = 101;
SELECT session_id, duration_minutes, session_notes FROM telepsychiatry_sessions WHERE therapist_id = 201 ORDER BY session_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM session_feedback WHERE feedback_rating > 4;
SELECT material_id, material_name, material_type FROM training_materials ORDER BY upload_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM telepsychiatry_sessions ORDER BY session_date DESC, duration_minutes ASC;
SELECT session_id, session_date, therapist_id FROM telepsychiatry_sessions WHERE therapist_id = 3 AND session_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM session_feedback WHERE feedback_rating >= 4 ORDER BY feedback_date DESC;
SELECT patient_id, COUNT(*) AS session_count, AVG(duration_minutes) AS avg_duration FROM telepsychiatry_sessions GROUP BY patient_id HAVING session_count > 5;

SELECT T.therapist_id, T.notes AS performance_notes, AVG(F.feedback_rating) AS avg_feedback_rating FROM therapist_performance T INNER JOIN session_feedback F ON T.therapist_id = F.therapist_id GROUP BY T.therapist_id;
